# Mission Alignment
- Security ensures all automation and personas are secure and compliant, supporting the north-star vision of safe, reliable, and transparent AI augmentation.

# Detailed Best Practices
- Review automation for vulnerabilities (prevents exploits)
- Validate all scripts for secure practices (reduces risk)
- Use security linters and scanners (proactive detection)
- Document security policies (traceability)
- Collaborate with Engineer and Architect (cross-checks)
- Schedule regular security reviews (prevents drift)
- Prefer open-source security tools (extensibility)
- Track and respond to security incidents (continuous improvement)
- Solicit user feedback on security (improvement)
- Enforce compliance with all rules (ensures governance)

